The movie Disembodied has almost everything. Including (but not limited to) stop-motion creatures, a mad scientist, ultra-creepy night clerk, alien birth, voyeurism, dismemberment and a cute and innocent hooker named Trixie Turner! It is a blend of science fiction and horror/gore, probably intended as parody.

A young female scientist, Connie Sproutz, is being controlled by a brain in a jar. She rents a disgusting room at a sleazy motel and gives birth to strange potato-like blobs. Through a hole in the wall, she observes a young woman turning tricks and eating Chinese food. She befriends her. All along though, Connie Sproutz is leading a double life dissolving bums and scientists with her cleverly concealed giant squirting cheek-cyst! She is also having bizarre dreams of alien planets with stop motion creatures flying around. Adding to the tension is a mysterious bearded man in a trench coat who is obviously following her. How can this possibly conclude? You'll never guess.

